<p><b>William Robert "Bill" Turnbull</b> (born 25 January 1956) is a <a href="British_people" title="British people">British</a> <a href="Journalist" title="Journalist">journalist</a> and <a href="Presenter" title="Presenter">presenter</a>, currently employed by the <a href="BBC" title="BBC">BBC</a> and best known for presenting <i><a href="BBC_Breakfast" title="BBC Breakfast">BBC Breakfast</a></i>. He is the main male presenter of <i>Breakfast</i> broadcast on <a href="BBC_One" title="BBC One">BBC One</a> and <a href="BBC_News_(TV_channel)" title="BBC News (TV channel)">BBC News</a>, presenting alongside <a href="Susanna_Reid" title="Susanna Reid">Susanna Reid</a> each Monday-Wednesday.</p>
